00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:34.180
Cobalah kabur kalau kau bisa!

00:07:44.390 --> 00:07:47.280
Nah, apa dia bisa lolos sekarang?

00:07:47.710 --> 00:07:49.930
Apa aku bisa remukkan
