00:09:23.500 --> 00:09:24.580
Jangan-jangan dia kabur?

00:09:25.790 --> 00:09:29.480
Kalau kapasitas paru-parunya besar,
bisa jadi

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:33.710
dia berenang melewati lorong-lorong
bawah tanah dan menuju kemari.

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:37.470
Takkan kubiarkan dia lolos!

